<b>Singing Short Sword Quest Walkthrough</b>
<blockquote>
A) Baldric Slezaf asks you for 4 items:
<ol>
<li>page 24 Top
<li>page 24 bottom 
<li>page 25 
<li>Lute made by Forper Fizfla 
</ol>
B) To get top part of page 24 (I will send 
update, these is the easy part of quest and 
can be done alone. I think you start in West 
Karana but I forget the NPCs name.)
<br><br>
C) To get the bottom half of you need to give 
Konia Swiftfoot Mahlin''s Bongos. Talk to 
Braenar Swiftsong. He will give you an 
invoice after you ask "what doll". Go to 
Solusek A and give the gnome vendor, 
Marfen the invoice and you will recieve a 
doll. Take the doll to the Estate of Unrest and 
give the doll to Serra, who is next to the 
gnomish speulunker. Serra will give you a 
note. Then take the note from Serra back to 
Braenar, who will give a new note for 
Maligar. Take the note from Braenar to 
Maligar. Maligar''s Enraged Doppleganger will 
attack at that point (bring a group). Kill the 
Doppleganger and loot his head. Take the head back to 
Braenar and recieve "Mahlin''s Bongo''s". 
Take the Bongo''s to Konia Swiftfoot in West 
Karana to get the bottom of Page 24. 
<br><br>
D) To get page 25 go to South Karana and 
talk to the woodelf bard Kelkin Mekia. She 
wants 3 items: 
<ol>
<li>Guts from a named chromatic drake in 
skyfire (Edrik the Old Level: 51 ) 
<li>Guts from the named wrum in Burning 
Woods (Nezekezena Level: 5? ); and 
<li>Guts from the Huge Oynx Drake in Rathe 
Mountains (Blackwing Level: 40 or so ) 
</ol>
Give these to her and you will get page 25 
<br><br>
E) Now you need Forpar''s Lute. This is 
rewarded as head, neck, body and strings. 
<br><br>
First you need to get horn from Ocean of 
Tears (Alluring horn from Quag Maelstrom). 
Take the alluring horn from Ocean of Tears 
to a half elf bard in Butcherblock, by the 
docks (Vedico). Take the note she gives you 
to Forpar. He then gives you a note and a list 
of items he needs: 
<ol>
<li>Backbone of an Ancient Fishman - 
Phnagel''s Spine from Kedge Keep 
<li>Amalgym Tentacle - Amygdalan Tendril 
from Plane of Fear 
<li>Petrified skull of a Lycanthrope - petrified 
werewolf skull from Karnor on Drolvarg 
Warlord 
</ol>
Take all 3 items and the note back give to 
Forpar and he gives you back the Head and 
Neck of the Lute ( a single item ) and the 
quest for the body, which requires the 
following items: 
<ol>
<li>Large red Dragon Scale (Talendor of 
Skyfire''s scale or Nagafen's) 
<li>Large white Dragon Scale (Gorenaire of 
Dreadlands or Vox's) 
<li>Two Metal bits (smithed metal bits) 
</ol>
Finally, get the strings for the Lute - 
Trakanon Gut Strings. These drop from 
Trakanon himself. 
<br><br>
Once you have all four, give following to 
Foplar to recieve the mystical lute: 
<ol>
<li>Head and neck 
<li>Body 
<li>Gut strings 
</ol>
I) You are almost there. To get your singing 
short sword give following items to Baldric 
Slezaf: 
<ol>
<li>Top of page 24 
<li>Bottom of page 24 
<li>Page 25 
<li>Mystical lute from Foplar 
</ol>
He will reward you with the Singing Short 
Sword
<br><br>
All items, with the exception of the 
Amygdalan Tendril, dragon scales and 
Trakanon Gut Strings, can be obtained with 2 
groups in the 50 to 55 level range helping 
you. 
<br><br>
<b><i>Quest Guide submitted by Tunela Deeda</i></b>
